Police are looking for a man who posed as a staff member in Defence Ministry and obtained over Sh26 million by false pretence. DavidÂ  Kahi Ambuku alias General is wanted by detectives following a warrant of arrest issued against him by Milimani Law Courts in Criminal Case No. 694/2018. DCI boss George Kinoti says that the fugitive is wanted for obtaining over Sh26 million by false pretences in a fake tender scheme. Kinoti called on citizens who might have information on David Ambuko's whereabouts to report to them. "Should you have any information regarding the above person, kindly contact us through our anonymous toll free number 0800722203," he said.